rComments: To be fair, the majority of your mark will be determined by your TA. Having said that, Dr. Khan is very approachable and gives you the tools you need to succeed in the course. Stay on top of things and it's very possible to succeed. Just don't underestimate the amount of time the post-labs take and prepare well for the labs.
